<p>Finally to verify the signature is valid, you&#8217;ll first create a message digest using the same process as above. Then hash each of the 160 numbers in the signature with RIPEMD160. Finally, check to make sure these hashes match the hashes in the <em>public key</em> that correspond with the message digest.</p>
<table>
<tbody>
<tr>
